  "description": "The language nerd in me has a lot of very critical thoughts about how we\u0026rsquo;re referring to the destruction of a flying gokart as a \u0026ldquo;kill\u0026rdquo;\nhttps://www.businessinsider.com/merops-middle-east-iran-drones-shaheds-surveyor-us-military-2026-3\nespecially given the whole, \u0026ldquo;are they replacing us with AI because there wont\u0026rsquo; be enough food for us in the climate broken future?\u0026rdquo;\nhaving media affirm the idea that what could be the replacements are capable of being killed - which implies they\u0026rsquo;re alive - seems\u0026hellip; like it would make it easier to avoid having any feelings at all about this, if you don\u0026rsquo;t perceive yourself as one fo the folk being threatened.\n",
